name: THE VIRTUAL MACHINE COLOSSUS
description: This well-known programmer gave us one of the world’s largest cryptocurrency exchange platform — Ethereum! Yes, that’s right, this titan is a tribute to the amazing Vitalik Buterin. He got featured in Forbes’ 30 under 30 list when he was just 23 years old back in 2018. In our NFT, we portrayed him as a supreme being, because let’s be honest, his achievements are divine!
